Increase YoutubeBridge cache TTL from 3h to 6h.

YouTube rate-limits automated requests to /feeds/videos.xml, producing
intermittent 404s when many feeds refresh simultaneously. Raising the
cache TTL halves request frequency while remaining responsive (channels
rarely post more than once a day).

Reference: https://github.com/RSS-Bridge/rss-bridge/issues/2113

--- a/bridges/YoutubeBridge.php
+++ b/bridges/YoutubeBridge.php
@@ -4,7 +4,7 @@
 {
     const NAME = 'YouTube';
     const URI = 'https://www.youtube.com';
-    const CACHE_TIMEOUT = 60 * 60 * 3;
+    const CACHE_TIMEOUT = 60 * 60 * 6; // 6 hours
     const DESCRIPTION = 'Returns the 10 newest videos by username/channel/playlist or search';

     const PARAMETERS = [
